  • Class Description
    Admin
    Admin is a subclass of User with a password attribute and a login method
    AdminControl
    Provides logic to perform admin functions
    AdminView
    Provides a view of the functions that an admin can perform
    BookingManager
    Makes movie booking for users
    Cinema
    Cinema refers to the theatre which movies will be played in
    CinemaControl
    Provides helper functions relating to cinemas
    Cineplex
    Cineplex is made up of multiple cinemas and movies with a unique location
    CineplexControl
    Provides helper functions relating to cineplexes
    CircularCinema
    CircularCinema refers to a cinema with a circular seating plan, similar to IMAX theatres
    Control
    Used to create other control classes for helper functions
    DateChecker
    Checks if the date is a public holiday or weekend
    DBManager
    DataBase Manager (DBManager) enables us to add new ways of saving data such as to a CSV file by extending from this interface
    GCCinema
    Gold Class Cinema is a RectangularCinema with its own number of rows and columns
    ImaxCinema
    IMAX Cinema is a RectangularCinema with its own number of rows and columns
    Initialiser
    Instantiates new data instead of loading previous state
    InputControl
    To check that user provides correct input
    MOBLIMA
    MOBLIMA loads/saves or instantiates new data and directs users to the correct view (UserView/AdminView)
    Movie
    Movie that will be shown in the cinema
    MovieControl
    Provides helper functions relating to movies
    MovieTicket
    Movie Ticket of a movie at a cineplex and cinema
    NormalCinema
    Normal cinema with a certain number of rows and columns
    Payment
    To authenticate payment
    Price
    Price class of a movie ticket
    RetangularCinema
    Cinema with a rectangular floorplan
    Review
    Review of movies
    ReviewManager
    Helper functions for users to add movie reviews
    SerializeDB
    Implements DBManager, enables loading and saving of data
    ShowtimeControl
    Provides helper functions relating to movie showtimes
    SortingManager
    Provides helper functions relating to sorting of movies
    TDCinema
    Three Dimensional Cinema (TDCinema) is a RectangularCinema
    User
    Normal user who can use the app to book tickets and other functionalities
    UserControl
    Provides logic to perform user functions
    UserView
    Provides a view of the functions that a normal user can perform
    VideoPlayer
    Additional feature which enables trailer to be played
    View
    Interface for other potential account views to be easily implemented: To easily add more boundaries/views to the application
